text:
	It is possible to gain extra privileges by overflowing buffer in
	dos_makepath().

	doscmd(1) is NOT suid/sgid by default.

Fix: 

Replace ustrcpy() and ustrcat() with strncpy() and strncat()
	in cwd.c:232.
